<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/64272299">30 岁被迫转行是一种怎样的体验？应如何应对？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="114126313"
data-atoken="462317280"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1533567548"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/64272299/answer/462317280">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="114126313">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="462317280">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-114126313"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>1189</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">1189</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
