<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/290003248">人生应该活成什么样子，该以什么样的方式活着？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="115825406"
data-atoken="471656305"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1534524626"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="0"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/290003248/answer/471656305">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="115825406">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="471656305">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-115825406"></a>

